{"tid":1424182,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【機場要成為主線任務！】和你飛文宣準備事宜","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:51:23.000Z","uid":272538,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d85d44afbbdab81bb4984cff57b6675be2b10fd2","tid":1424182,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"因應呢兩個post我覺得我哋必須要加強機場呢條文宣線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">【唔好搞罷工太密！民航署可能係救香港唯一出路】</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1416184/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1416184/page/1</a> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">【...最快一年內，香港人這概念會被剷除。一場社會文化改造，正在發生。】</span></span></strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1396835/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1396835/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n雖然星期五先係第二次機場接機，但我哋必須要爭分奪秒繼續提醒所有人我哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">作為香港人</span></strong></span>嘅初衷！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以有兩樣好重要嘅嘢要考慮：</strong><br />\n1）因為發生咗好多次我哋已經<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平常化</span></span>政府講大話、警察濫權、同採訪嘅自由被剝削！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2）機場真係一個政府無敢講同警察唔敢清場嘅地方，簡直係一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">和理非勝地</span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一點好重要嘅，因為若果我哋被人溫水煮蛙咁對鎮壓者<span style=\"color: red;\">麻木</span>，攞唔攞到五大訴求都好，我哋將會陷入<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">道德淪亡</span></strong>嘅困局。<br />\n<br />\n好似樓主所講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「係咁架啦」＋「仲可以點」 ＝ 自暴自棄，道德淪亡</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二點好簡單，要有效地對政府同香港嘅經濟施壓！機場就係最安全<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最有效益</span></span></strong>嘅和理非活動，若然我哋連呢樣嘢都做得唔好，我哋<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">冇辦法輔助到前線手足做到嘅嘢</span></strong>。所以一定要做！一定要做文宣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDgCUv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDgCUv7.jpg&h=9ba524e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我提議喺<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">荔景</span></strong>同<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>機場</strong></span>嘅返工放工時間舉下牌。五大訴求都唔使重點講，最緊要係提醒大家我哋唔可以對呢啲當權者嘅行為麻木。市民可以對圍警署、佔路或者掟嘢有唔同意見，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係無一個香港人會縱容警務人員無視自己工作守則，政府官員敷衍市民轉移視線，唔比我哋睇到事情發生嘅真相！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋要馬上做！標語／簡單文宣即刻做！"},{"pid":"959ec87113c42561bcc4289676c891e94afb2fe9","tid":1424182,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4c025344255ffc7f0c7e8ae2cf652b0932a20234","tid":1424182,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3688a253db5f0b50b32860503bf9163fa332be4","tid":1424182,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c025344255ffc7f0c7e8ae2cf652b0932a20234","tid":1424182,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1414005/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1414005/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b9dc061667c786a91a73f256e6853626bac29e46","tid":1424182,"u